[Croutons Recipe]
Ingredients: Bread,Olive Oil,Salt,Pepper
Step 1: Cut the bread into 1.5 x 1.5 cm cubes
Step 2: Place frying pan over medium to high heat
Step 3: Place bread cubes into frying pan
Step 4: Drizzle olive oil over bread cubes
Step 5: Fry bread cubes, mixing frequently, until golden brown
Step 6: Season to taste
